name: Roboto Factory - Part Five
description:
We have experienced worrying moments. The team of scientists, after having completed the first phase of Robotas had a conflict with Brainstorming to start the second phase. The working community confronted the prototypes to be built and a strike was called.
After an intense dialogue between the Dao and the workers' leaders, a vote was taken that ended with the agreement of both parties. Everything will continue to go "from strength to strength" at Robotos Factory Inc.
